# Purpose:
#   Provide a complete index of all operational workflows in the cluster,
#   linking diagnostics, build steps, deployment steps, and recovery steps.
#
# Workflow Categories:
#
#   1. Build Workflows
#      - Prechecks
#      - Build lifecycle
#      - Postchecks
#      - Promotion
#
#   2. Deployment Workflows
#      - Kernel rollout
#      - Rollback
#      - Node-by-node update
#
#   3. Diagnostics Workflows
#      - Kernel reports
#      - Network reports
#      - Filesystem reports
#
#   4. Recovery Workflows
#      - Incident response
#      - Rollback-first strategy
#
# Notes:
#   - This file is the authoritative workflow map for the entire system.
